---

## Risks

| Risk | Mitigation |
|---|---|
| tau drops too much from stale context | Phase D4 adaptive bypass; per-genre threshold |
| KV cache write race | verify N writes target KV; draft uses its own - no shared writes (audited in original PRD line 142-160) |
| hidden_rb read race | Use last-committed slot which is >=1 cycle old - never written concurrently |
| Stream creation cost | One-time per session; amortized |
| Coherence-gate fails | Fall back to sequential; investigate as numerical bug not perf opt |

---

## Out of scope

- Multi-step pipelining (draft N+2 ahead of verify N) - exponential mis-prediction blast radius
- Cross-arch validation (BC-250, MI300X) - gfx1100 first
- Path C (training-based oracle revival) - separate PRD: `docs/plans/task-93-path-c-trained-draft.prd`

